data/cache.db
data/cache.db-*
*.parquet
# Cloud cold-start seeds used to live under `data/seed/` and ship in
# git, but HF Spaces rejects every binary file (any size, not just
# >10MB) without Xet/LFS — so the IAS history bundle is downloaded at
# Docker build time instead (see Dockerfile). Keep this directory
# gitignored so a local dev cache can land here without being staged.
data/seed/

